org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.components.FCM

Interface FCMPackage.Literals

  • Enclosing interface:
    FCMPackage

    public static interface FCMPackage.Literals
    Defines literals for the meta objects that represent
    • each class,
    • each feature of each class,
    • each enum,
    • and each data type
